Sub-Cat to Com-Cat: Update Start and End Dates

Calculator
Parameter
Value
Include Input Columns
Yes
Calculations
Cast("last_updated" as date), last_updated, CASE WHEN to_char(cast("efftv_start_dt" as date), 'dd') <> '01'
OR ( to_char(dateadd(day,1,cast(efftv_end_dt as date)), 'dd') <> '01'
AND cast(efftv_end_dt as date) <> '12/31/9999') THEN
'Info'
ELSE
''
END, status, CASE WHEN to_char(cast("efftv_start_dt" as date), 'dd') <> '01' THEN
'Info-Update the effective start date to the first day of month.'
WHEN to_char(dateadd(day,1,cast(efftv_end_dt as date)), 'dd') <> '01'
AND cast(efftv_end_dt as date) <> '12/31/9999' THEN
'Info-Update the effective start date to the last day of month.'
ELSE
''
END, reason, CASE WHEN to_char(cast("efftv_start_dt" as date), 'dd') <> '01' THEN
cast(to_char(cast("efftv_start_dt" as date), 'mm') || '/' ||
'01/' ||
to_char(cast("efftv_start_dt" as date), 'yyyy') as date)
ELSE
cast("efftv_start_dt" as date)
END
, efftv_start_dt, CASE WHEN (to_char(cast("efftv_end_dt" as date), 'yyyy') = '9999' AND
to_char(cast("efftv_end_dt" as date), 'mm') = '12') THEN
cast('12/31/9999' as date)
WHEN to_char(dateadd(day,1,cast("efftv_end_dt" as date)), 'dd') <> '01' THEN
cast(last_day(cast("efftv_end_dt" as date)) as date)
ELSE
cast("efftv_end_dt" as date)

END

, efftv_end_dt, to_char(dateadd(day,1,cast("efftv_end_dt" as date)), 'dd'), new_efftv_end_dt, CASE WHEN cast("efftv_start_dt" as date) < cast('01/01/2019' as date) THEN
cast('01/01/2019' as date)
ELSE
cast("efftv_start_dt" as date)
END, new_efftv_start_dt

Job: Archive Outbound Global Function

Add TimeStamp & Get File,Table Information from context of the job run

Python Script
Parameter
Value
Script
import datetime

x = datetime.datetime.now()
x=str(x).split('.')

x=x[0]
print('time_stamp :'+str(x))
print('Archive_temp_current_table :'+str(Archive_temp_current_table))
print('Archive_temp_current_file :'+str(Archive_temp_current_file))

Archive_temp_current_file=Archive_temp_current_file+'_'+x+'__'
print('Archive_temp_current_file upt :'+str(Archive_temp_current_file))
context.updateVariable('Archive_temp_current_file', str(Archive_temp_current_file))
print('Archive_type :'+Archive_type)


#dynamically change path for Archive
if Archive_type=='ONEMD':
S3_temp_Archive_Location=S3_ONEMD_Archive_Location
print('Archive Locations :'+str(S3_temp_Archive_Location))
elif Archive_type=='MDM21':
S3_temp_Archive_Location=S3_MDM21_Archive_Location
print('Archive Locations :'+str(S3_temp_Archive_Location))
else:
S3_temp_Archive_Location=S3_EUSS_Archive_Location
print('Archive Locations :'+str(S3_temp_Archive_Location))
